histograma <- function(x) {
  min <- min(x, na.rm = TRUE)
  max <- max(x, na.rm = TRUE)
  media <- mean(x, na.rm = TRUE)
  mediana <- median(x, na.rm = TRUE)
  dt <- sd(x, na.rm = TRUE)
  
  hist(x, freq = F)
  lines(density(x, na.rm = TRUE),
        lwd = 2,
        col = "chocolate3")
  
  abline(v = media,
         col = "royalblue",
         lwd = 2)
  
  abline(v = mediana,
         col = "red",
         lwd = 2)
  
  legend(
    x = "topright",
    c("Density plot", "Mean", "Median"),
    col = c("chocolate3", "royalblue", "red"),
    lwd = c(2, 2, 2)
  )
}
